'''Ɛisa''' ([[Taɛebrit]] : ישוע‎, ''yacuɛ'') neɣ '''Ɛisa n Nazarit''' neɣ '''Ɛisa Amasiḥ''', d amdan amenzawi n [[ajjed]] n [[tamasiḥit]]. Ilul ger 8 d sin iseggasen send tazwara n tafada tameɣradant , yemmut ger 30 d 33 iseggasen umbeɛd. Isem-is daɣen 'Jesus-Christ' neɣ s wudem aḥerfi 'Christ'. S [[tayunanit|tyunanit]] taqburt isem-is Ιησούς Χριστός (''Iesous Khristos''). 

Aẓaṛ n wawal Ɛisa yusa-d si [[Taɛebrit|tutlayt taɛebrit]] : ישוע‎ neɣ - ''yacuɛ'', anamek ines d "Yehweh (rebbi) isellek". Ma d Aẓaṛ n wawal "Amasiḥ" d wawal n taɛebrit  משיח - ''macyaḥ'', neɣ win ɣef d-ters tanebaṭ n '''''[[Rebbi]].''''' 

Imasiḥiyen ḥesben-t d afessi akk d mmi-s n Rebbi. Wid yellan d 'Ikatulikiyen', d 'urtuduksiyen', akk d 'ibrutistaniyen' ttadren-t-id am wergaz n tidett, u daɣen d Rebbi s tidett. Ɣur yinselmen Ɛisa d aneggaru deg wsar beɛd [[Muḥemmed]]. Ma d udayen, ur t-ḥsiben ara d rrasul, wala d Afessi neɣ mmis n Yakuc. 

